# Scholarly Gateway - User Guide

## Welcome to Publications Portal

This portal provides access to research publications from various institutions. Search and browse scholarly publications, research papers, and academic works.

---

## How to Search

### Basic Search
1. Enter your search term in the search box at the top
2. Press Enter or click Search
3. Browse results sorted by year (newest first)

### Search Fields
You can search by:
- **Title** - Publication title
- **Author** - Author name
- **Source** - Journal or conference name

Example: `machine learning` will find all publications containing these words

---

## Using Filters

### Filter by Year
- **Individual Years**: Click checkboxes to select specific years
- **Year Range**: Use the slider to select a range (e.g., 2020-2024)

### Filter by Type
Select publication types:
- Article
- Conference Paper
- Book Chapter
- Thesis
- Report

### Filter by Department
Select departments from the available options

### Filter by Author
Select specific authors to see their publications

### Filter by Language
Select publication language:
- English
- Hindi
- Other languages

### Filter by Country
Select countries where research was published

### Filter by Source
Select journals or conferences

### Filter by Open Access
Select open access status:
- Gold Open Access
- Green Open Access
- Closed Access

---

## Multiple Filters

You can combine multiple filters:
1. Select "Article" from Type
2. Select "2024" from Year
3. Select "Computer Science" from Department

The portal will show only publications that match ALL selected filters.

---

## Understanding Results

### Result Display
Each result shows:
- **Title** - Publication title (clickable)
- **Authors** - Author names
- **Year** - Publication year
- **Type** - Publication type
- **Journal/Conference** - Where published
- **DOI** - Digital Object Identifier (clickable)

### Links
- Click title to view full publication in repository
- Click DOI to view on publisher website

---

## Pagination

### Results Per Page
You can change number of results shown:
- 25 (default)
- 50
- 100
- 500

### Navigation
- Use Previous/Next buttons
- Click page numbers to jump directly

---

## Facet Modal (See More)

When there are many filter options:
1. Click "See More" or "View All" button
2. A popup modal appears with all options
3. Search within the modal to find specific values
4. Select multiple options
5. Click Apply to filter

---

## Exporting Results

You can export search results in different formats:
1. Select a format from the Export dropdown (CSV, JSON, or Text)
2. The export will include all records matching your current filters
3. File will download automatically

### Export Formats
- **CSV** - Comma-separated values (Excel compatible)
- **JSON** - JavaScript Object Notation (for developers)
- **Text** - Tab-separated plain text

---

## URL Sharing

You can share your search results:
1. Apply your filters
2. Copy the URL from browser address bar
3. Send to colleague
4. They will see same results with same filters

---

## Tips

### Finding Specific Author
1. Type author name in search box, OR
2. Use Author filter and type name in modal

### Finding Recent Publications
1. Set Year filter to desired range
2. Results automatically sorted by newest first

### Finding Open Access Articles
1. Use Open Access filter
2. Select "Gold" or "Green"

---

## Troubleshooting

### No Results Found
- Try broader search terms
- Check spelling
- Remove some filters

### Too Many Results
- Add more specific filters
- Use search with keywords

### Page Not Loading
- Check internet connection
- Try refreshing the page
- Clear browser cache

---

## Quick Reference

| Feature | How to Use |
|---------|------------|
| Search | Type in search box |
| Filter by Year | Checkboxes or slider |
| Filter by Type | Select from list |
| Filter by Department | Select departments |
| Change Results Per Page | Dropdown selector |
| Export Results | Select format from dropdown |
| Share Results | Copy URL |
| View Full Publication | Click title |
| View Publisher Site | Click DOI |

